post_text:
Today the Bearkats and Lady Kats competed in the Odessa Permian JV Golf Tournament. It was a very successful day! Five of our golfers had personal best tournament scores.

Three of our Lady Kats competed today. Logan Wood shot 81 to win the tournament. Claire Fuchs shot a personal best with a 93 and finished 3rd. Jaedon Gass shot her personal best with a 109.

The Bearkats won the tournament! Nick Lara shot even par 72 (a personal best) to win the tournament. Dakota Roberts also shot a personal best with a 74 to finish 2nd.
Ryan Halfmann shot a personal best of 87 and finally Seth Lara shot a 92. Congratulations to all golfers!
